{
  "id": 5073740211814400,
  "name": "Multicast support for Direct Sockets API",
  "summary": "This feature allows [Isolated Web Apps](https://chromeos.dev/en/web/isolated-web-apps) (IWAs) to subscribe to multicast groups and receive User Datagram Protocol (UDP) packets from there. IWAs can now also specify additional parameters when sending UDP packets to multicast addresses.",
